# CODEOWNERS
#
# Phase 6 of docs/slo-roadmap.md. Enforces review on the small set of
# paths whose misconfiguration has outsized blast radius. Deliberately
# narrow — requiring CODEOWNER review on every markdown change would
# just train reviewers to rubber-stamp.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <@owner> [<@owner> ...]
# Patterns follow .gitignore globbing; last-match wins.
#
# IMPORTANT: replace the `@OWNER` placeholder below with the GitHub
# user or team that should review changes to hot paths. If this file
# lands in a fork without a real handle, GitHub silently skips
# CODEOWNER review — which defeats the point. Use a team (e.g.
# `@your-org/infra`) rather than a single user wherever possible.

# Default: all changes reviewable by the designated owner.
*                                                @OWNER

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Hard requirements — must have CODEOWNER review, no self-merge.
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# All Terraform: state mutations ship through here.
/terraform/                                      @OWNER

# State bucket bootstrap: misconfig here makes state unrecoverable.
/terraform/bootstrap/                            @OWNER

# Cloud SQL as code: touches the data tier.
/terraform/cloud_sql.tf                          @OWNER

# CI workflows: a broken workflow masks every other check.
/.github/workflows/                              @OWNER

# Required-secrets inventory + deploy gate.
/.github/workflows/deploy.yml                    @OWNER

# Startup script: the VM's entire bootstrap logic lives here.
/scripts/startup.sh                              @OWNER

# Image digest pinning: supply-chain trust anchor.
/scripts/refresh-digests.sh                      @OWNER

# Incident response playbooks — wrong procedure is worse than no
# procedure.
/Runbook.md                                      @OWNER
/docs/postmortems/                               @OWNER
/docs/oncall.md                                  @OWNER
/docs/error-budget-policy.md                     @OWNER
/docs/drills/                                    @OWNER
